# Coffee Sales Dashboard

## Project Overview
This Power BI dashboard analyzes coffee shop sales performance across products, weekdays, and time periods to identify revenue trends and customer purchasing behavior.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Excel
- Data Cleaning
- Data Visualization

## Key KPIs
- Total Sales Amount: ₹112.25K
- Product-wise Revenue Analysis
- Weekday Sales Distribution
- Time-of-Day Sales Analysis

## Features
- Interactive slicers for Month and Weekday
- Product performance tracking
- Sales trend analysis
- Customer purchase pattern insights

## Business Insights
- Identified top-performing coffee products.
- Analyzed sales distribution across weekdays.
- Compared Morning, Afternoon, and Night sales patterns.
- Enabled interactive exploration of sales data.


